| #1 | TopologyMetadata | `pauseTopology()` | Missing signal to wake state updater on topology pause | CRITICAL |
| #2 | DefaultStateUpdater | `pauseTask()`, `resumeTask()`, `maybeCompleteRestoration()` | State changes without signalling condition | HIGH |
| #3 | DefaultStateUpdater | `shutdown()` | Only signals `tasksAndActionsCondition`, not `restoredActiveTasksCondition` | MEDIUM |
